headline: Unum (UNM) Lags Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: Unum (UNM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -7.17% and +1.72%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Analysts Estimate Aflac (AFL) to Report a Decline in Earnings: What to Look Out for
summary: Aflac (AFL) doesn't possess the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely earnings beat in its upcoming report. Get prepared with the key expectations.
